##Fill inventory
execute as @a[tag=player] run function 4jglide:game/inventory/fill

##Clear hotbar of books
execute as @a[tag=player] run function 4jglide:game/inventory/clear

##Delete dropped books
kill @e[type=item,nbt={Item:{tag:{SmallInv:1}}}]

##Clear chests
#Center
execute as @e[tag=CenterChest] at @s if data block ~ ~ ~ {Items:[{id:"minecraft:knowledge_book"}]} run function 4jglide:game/inventory/clearchest
#Standard
execute as @e[tag=StandardChest] at @s if data block ~ ~ ~ {Items:[{id:"minecraft:knowledge_book"}]} run function 4jglide:game/inventory/clearchest

##Loop
schedule function 4jglide:game/inventory/check 3t